					</a>
				</p>
					<a href="20250421-the-family.html">
						<img src="img/digital/20250421-the-family.png" alt="Three people — one of them with three arms — gather beneath a twisting, leafless tree." loading="lazy"><br/>The Family
					</a>
				</p>
				<p>I'm hard at work on some longer projects that won't see release for some time, but you can always find some <a href="https://www.patreon.com/helveticablanc" target="_blank">sneak peeks on my Patreon</a>!</p>
				]]>
